==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quitch
<hw>Quitch</hw> <pr>(kw⟦icr⟧ch)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Same as <er>Quitch grass</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Figuratively: A vice; a taint; an evil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To pick the vicious <qex>quitch</qex>⟦br⟧
Of blood and custom wholly out of him.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quitch grass</ent>⟦br⟧
